posts.post_title: *SOLD* T205 T206 ST. LOUIS subsets: 49 cards *SOLD*
posts.post_content:
Over a few years I took the time to build complete subsets from the T205 and T206 set.  The T205 consists of all the St. Louis Cardinals cards (except the Bresnahan Open Mouth variation).  The T205 subsets consist of all St. Louis Cardinals and Browns cards.  The total number of cards are 49 in this subset.  On top of collection St. Louis cards, I also focused on getting a variety of ad backs.  I don't have any of the really rare backs but I do have two Carolina Brights and one Brown Hindu.  I'll provide links to my photobucket with all the ad backs and front scans of all the cards.  Most cards are RAW but a couple are graded.  I'd grade the overall quality of the lot to be VG.
